OOC:Is the Dark Avian a typical Decepticon cruiser?

BIC:

Ragnus looked about as he entered the base, alert for any sign of a 
trap.  Moving down the hallways of the base with relative speed, he 
searched for a computer terminal in every room he passed.  After 
almost five minutes of searching his efforts bore fruit, as he found 
what he was looking for, One of the secondary computer rooms.

Kneeling before the terminal he Keyed in his decepticon tactical 
acces code that is hardwired into most decepticon vehicals.  

The computer flashed a message across the screen.

***Enter user identification:***

He typed in his full access name.

***G1 Proto Ragnus 7317***

***Processing.........***
